  <metadata>
    <id>solomd</id>
    <version>1.2.1</version>
    <title>SoloMD</title>
    <authors>xiangdong li</authors>
    <owners>zhitongblog</owners>
    <licenseUrl>https://github.com/zhitongblog/solomd/blob/main/LICENSE</licenseUrl>
    <projectUrl>https://solomd.app</projectUrl>
    <iconUrl>https://solomd.app/favicon.svg</iconUrl>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <description>
SoloMD is a lightweight, cross-platform Markdown + plain text editor built with Tauri 2.

## Features
- Live preview (WYSIWYG-style editing)
- KaTeX math rendering
- Mermaid diagrams
- Multi-encoding support (UTF-8, GBK, Big5)
- Export to PDF, DOCX, HTML
- Light &amp; dark themes
- Clean AI artifacts (remove citations from ChatGPT/Claude)
- Only 15MB installer

## Why SoloMD?
One file. One window. Just write.
    </description>
    <summary>A lightweight Markdown editor with live preview</summary>
